    <sec id="Sec18">
      <title>Statistics</title>
      <p id="Par58">When testing each of the <inline-formula id="IEq82"><alternatives><tex-math id="M179">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
